snippet.title: Monster Energy Supercross - The Official Videogame 2 - Announcement Trailer
snippet.description: Live like a real champion with Monster Energy Supercross - The Official Videogame 2. Success is not just about winning: train hard, meet fans, find new sponsors and contracts, this is the winning formula to become the greatest rider. Out on February 8th 2019 on PS4, Xbox One, PC/Steam and Nintendo Switch: https://supercrossthegame.com
